		{"id":"1e8769548a2c15d0","type":"text","text":"# Idees pour le futur\n- ## **JSON** storage ✅ implémenté\n\t- `PlayerSave.java` : stocke hero, inventaire, flags\n\t- `SaveManager.java` : sérialisation Gson avec désérialiseurs custom\n\t- Fichiers dans `users_info/<nom>.json`\n- ## Effets de statut ❌ pas implémentés\n\t- ### Poison\n\t- ### Feu\n\t- ### ...","x":460,"y":1740,"width":465,"height":309},
		{"id":"491024cc3bb92527","type":"file","file":"POO/2026-04-08-features.md","x":1240,"y":1740,"width":760,"height":840},
		{"id":"98590e452fff9958","type":"file","file":"POO/Json implementation (ShadowArena).md","x":0,"y":2640,"width":712,"height":640},
		{"id":"hero_stats_node","type":"text","text":"# Stats des héros (valeurs réelles)\n| Héros | HP | Mana | ATQ | Coût SPE |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Mage | 400 | 600 | 40 | 80 mana |\n| Knight | 450 | 600 | 35 | 80 mana |\n| Berserker | 500 | 200 | 50+ | 100 mana |\n\n- **Défense** : 60 mana → bloque 100% dégâts 1 tour\n- **XP par monstre** : 50 pts → level up à 150 XP\n- **Level up** : +5 ATQ, +20 HP max, +10 Mana max","x":840,"y":-480,"width":560,"height":480},
		{"id":"hierarchy_node","type":"text","text":"# Hiérarchie des classes (POO)\n## GameCharacter (abstraite)\n- → Hero (abstraite)\n\t- → Mage (impl. MageAbilities)\n\t- → Knight (impl. KnightAbilities)\n\t- → Berserker (impl. BerserkerAbilities)\n- → Monster (abstraite)\n\t- → Goblin | GiantSnake | Troll | Cerberus | Dragon\n\n## GameItem (abstraite)\n- → AttackItem → Grenade\n- → HealingItem → Potion | ManaPotion\n- → BuffItem → Amulette","x":-2080,"y":-480,"width":560,"height":480},
